description: Retrieves a list of resources of the specified type that have been analyzed by the specified analyzer.

parameters.name: analyzerArn
parameters.description: The ARN of the analyzer to retrieve a list of analyzed resources from. The ARN of the analyzer to retrieve a list of analyzed resources from.

parameters.name: nextToken
parameters.description: A token used for pagination of results returned.

parameters.name: maxResults
parameters.description: The maximum number of results to return in the response.

nested_items.name: analyzedResources
nested_items.description: A list of resources that were analyzed.

nested_items.name: resourceArn
nested_items.description: The ARN of the analyzed resource.

nested_items.name: resourceOwnerAccount
